    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/9cfb738277de6e4b587c4415413bc760.poster.avif?t=1699631951\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/9cfb738277de6e4b587c4415413bc760.webm?t=1699631951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/9cfb738277de6e4b587c4415413bc760.mp4?t=1699631951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You control a <strong>Qubit</strong>, an <i>Artificially Intelligent Quantum Bit</i>, deep within a Learning Interface of a Quantum Computer, completing <strong>Trials</strong> of intelligence, speed, and patience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Qubit is <i>not</i> alone.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/02d991dbca2369902e661e3034232bd7.poster.avif?t=1699631951\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/02d991dbca2369902e661e3034232bd7.webm?t=1699631951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/02d991dbca2369902e661e3034232bd7.mp4?t=1699631951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Encounter <strong>the Sage</strong>, a <strong>Superintelligent</strong>, all knowing entity who has mastered the Infinite, and is now here to guide you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/9b1f448ef49d5d521d59505308ed0262.poster.avif?t=1699631951\" width=628 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/9b1f448ef49d5d521d59505308ed0262.webm?t=1699631951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1697070/extras/9b1f448ef49d5d521d59505308ed0262.mp4?t=1699631951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Talk with various employees of <strong>Bree Inc</strong>, a Corporation that will harness the power of AI no matter the cost, through <strong>Distortions</strong> in the Learning Interface.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Qubit is <i>frail</i>.</h2>The Trials are not a pleasant place for the Qubit, and death is always around. From <strong>Black Holes</strong> to <strong>Shooters</strong>, <strong>Lasers</strong> and <strong>Bombs</strong>, to the <strong>Walls</strong> that surround the Trials themselves, hazards are everywhere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A Story Mode with many Trials, twists and turns, and multiple endings.<br></li><li> An Arcade Mode to hone your skills and get the best times on the global Steam Leaderboard.</li></ul>",
